      <title>银行关注 Reddit IPO，着眼于承销反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-21/banks-watch-reddit-ipo-with-eye-on-underwriting-rebound-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社的 Amy Or 报道，Reddit Inc. 只是今年美国第四大首次公开募股，但它是华尔街银行关注的焦点，它们希望 IPO 市场及其承销费用的低迷已经结束。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-21/banks-watch-reddit-ipo-with-eye-on-underwriting-rebound-video</guid>
